---  
description: Route Sitecore XM Cloud tasks to the right Cursor skill.  
alwaysApply: false  
---  
  
When a Sitecore task is requested, classify it first:  
  
1. Simple datasource component  
- one datasource item  
- no Sitecore child datasource items  
- no ComponentQuery  
- use skill: `sitecore-create-simple-component`  
  
2. List / parent-child datasource component  
- parent datasource has child items  
- requires ComponentQuery  
- requires _HorizonDatasourceGrouping on parent template  
- use skill: `sitecore-create-list-component`  
  
3. Context-only component  
- no datasource  
- reads route fields from page context  
  
4. Debug / repair  
- datasource picker empty  
- bad ComponentQuery  
- variant issues  
- props shape mismatch  
  
Before execution, fill the shared spec template:  
`.cursor/skills/_shared/sitecore-component-spec.template.yaml`  